B.Os=new A.db("How do I access the menu to order food?","You'll receive an SMS or WhatsApp message with a link as your bus approaches the rest stop. Tap the link to open the food ordering page \u2014 no app download or login needed.")
B.Oq=new A.db("When will I receive the booking link?","The link is sent approximately 2 to 3 hours before your bus reaches the restaurant, so you have enough time to browse the menu and place your order comfortably.")
B.Oh=new A.db("Do I need to create an account to order?","No. The system automatically identifies you using your mobile number and booking details. Just tap the link and you're in.")
B.O9=new A.db("Can I add special instructions to my order?",'Yes. At checkout, there is an optional notes field where you can mention preferences like "less spicy" or any dietary requests.')
B.Ol=new A.db("What happens after I place my order?","You'll receive an Order ID and a QR code on screen. Show this to the restaurant counter staff when you arrive to collect your food.")
B.RL=s([B.Os,B.Oq,B.Oh,B.O9,B.Ol],t.Cx)
B.Oy=new A.lV("How to book a meal?",B.RL)
B.Om=new A.db("What payment methods are accepted?","You can pay via UPI, debit/credit card, and other available digital payment options shown at checkout.")
B.O8=new A.db("My payment failed. What should I do?","If your payment fails, you'll see an option to retry on screen. You'll also receive an SMS/WhatsApp with a retry link. Try again using a different payment method if the issue persists.")
B.Oj=new A.db("Was I charged even though my order didn't go through?","If the payment failed, no amount will be deducted. If your bank shows a deduction but the order wasn't confirmed, the amount will be reversed automatically within 5\u20137 business days depending on your bank.")
B.O5=new A.db("Is my payment information secure?","Yes. All transactions are encrypted and processed through a secure payment gateway. We do not store your card or UPI details.")
B.Tf=s([B.Om,B.O8,B.Oj,B.O5],t.Cx)
B.Ot=new A.lV("Payment Issues",B.Tf)
B.O2=new A.db("Can I cancel my order?","Order cancellation is not available at this time. Please review your order carefully before confirming payment.")
B.Oi=new A.db("What if I change my mind after ordering?","Since cancellations are not currently supported, we recommend double-checking your items before placing the order. If you have an urgent issue, please use the Help & Support option to contact the restaurant or our support team directly.")
B.SV=s([B.O2,B.Oi],t.Cx)
B.Ow=new A.lV("Order Cancellation",B.SV)
B.Oa=new A.db("Under what circumstances will I get a refund?","Refunds are currently only applicable in cases where your payment was deducted but the order was not confirmed due to a technical or payment gateway error.")
B.Or=new A.db("How long does a refund take?","Refunds are processed within 5\u20137 business days and credited back to your original payment method.")
B.Og=new A.db("How will I know if my refund has been processed?","You will receive an SMS or WhatsApp notification once the refund is initiated from bank. You can also check with your bank or UPI app for the credit status.")
B.Ob=new A.db("Who do I contact if I haven't received my refund?",'Please reach out to our support team using the "Call Support" option on the app or raise a complaint under Help & Support.')
B.Sq=s([B.Oa,B.Or,B.Og,B.Ob],t.Cx)
B.Oz=new A.lV("Refund Process",B.Sq)
B.On=new A.db("I didn't receive the booking link. What should I do?","Please check your SMS inbox and WhatsApp. If you still don't see the link, ensure your registered mobile number with the bus operator is correct. You can also contact the support number provided by your bus operator.")
B.Od=new A.db("The link I received is not opening. What do I do?","Make sure you have an active internet connection. The link works best on Chrome or Safari. If the link shows as expired, it may have timed out \u2014 please contact support.")
B.O0=new A.db("My mobile number was not auto-detected. What happens?","Your order access is tied to the mobile number you used when booking your bus ticket. If there's a mismatch, please contact support for assistance.")
B.QL=s([B.On,B.Od,B.O0],t.Cx)
B.OA=new A.lV("Account Issues",B.QL)
B.Oo=new A.db("How do I know the restaurant is hygienic?","Each restaurant's profile shows google customer reviews, and photos of the restrooms, food, and ambience \u2014 so you can make an informed choice before ordering.")
B.Ok=new A.db("What if the food quality was not as expected?","You can submit a rating and feedback after collecting your order. Your feedback goes directly to the restaurant and our team to ensure quality is maintained.")
B.Oc=new A.db("Can I report a hygiene concern immediately?","Yes. Use Help & Support option to flag hygiene, food quality, or service issues. Our team will be notified immediately.")
B.Ta=s([B.Oo,B.Ok,B.Oc],t.Cx)
B.Ox=new A.lV("Food Quality & Hygiene",B.Ta)
B.O6=new A.db("How do I collect my order at the restaurant?","Once you arrive at the restaurant, show your QR code or OTP to the counter staff or your mobile number. They will verify and hand over your order.")
B.Op=new A.db("What if I lose my QR code or OTP?","The restaurant staff can also verify your order using your registered mobile number. Just provide it at the counter.")
B.O7=new A.db("What if my order is not ready when I arrive?","Your estimated preparation time is shown on the order tracking screen. If there's a delay, please check with the restaurant counter staff directly.")
B.O1=new A.db("Can someone else collect my order on my behalf?","The order is verified by QR code, OTP, or mobile number. If you share these details with someone, they can collect on your behalf.")
B.Ti=s([B.O6,B.Op,B.O7,B.O1],t.Cx)
B.Ov=new A.lV("Delivery & Pickup",B.Ti)
B.Oe=new A.db("Which restaurants are available on CleanStop?","The restaurant shown to you is the designated rest stop assigned to your bus route by your bus operator. You'll see full details \u2014 name, location, ratings, and menu \u2014 when you tap your booking link.")
B.Of=new A.db("Can I see the restaurant before my bus departs?","The restaurant details and menu become accessible once your trip is active and the booking link is sent to you, typically 2 to 3 hours before the rest stop.")
B.O3=new A.db("How do I give feedback about my experience?","After collecting your order, you'll receive a feedback request via SMS or WhatsApp. You can rate your experience on food quality, hygiene, and service, and leave optional comments.")
B.O4=new A.db("Who do I contact for other issues?",'Use the "Call Support" option in Help & Support to reach our customer care team, or raise a complaint through the app.')
B.Te=s([B.Oe,B.Of,B.O3,B.O4],t.Cx)
B.Ou=new A.lV("General Inquiry",B.Te)
B.Sk=s([B.Oy,B.Ot,B.Ow,B.Oz,B.OA,B.Ox,B.Ov,B.Ou],A.ao("u<lV>"))
